    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years or older

          -  Primary Diagnostic and Statistical Manual, Fifth Edition (DSM-5) diagnosis of
             Trichotillomania (TTM)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Current suicidality or severe depression

